text: Transaction Behavior The agent does not emit or retrieve any commands. Input/Output Data The input/output data is the type of data an agent expects and delivers. The agent consumes selected UDR types. MIM For information about the MIM and a list of the general MIM parameters, see Administration and Management in Legacy Desktop . Publishes MIM Value Description Agent Name The name of the agent. Inbound UDRs The number of UDRs routed to the agent. Accesses The agent does not itself access any MIM resources. Agent Message Events There are no agent message events for this agent. Debug Events There are no debug events for this agent.
